text: Cornufer mamusiorum is a frog. Scientists have seen it in exactly one place: the Nakanai Mountains in Papua New Guinea. People have seen it more than 1500 meters above sea level. The adult male frog is about 27.4 to 30.7 mm long from nose to rear end. This frog lives in rainforests in the mountains. ==References== Category:Frogs of Oceania
title: Cornufer mamusiorum
